{"tid":1303165,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【40年前】翁靜晶15歲曾任寶礦力代言人，當年廣告由CCTVB樂易玲接洽。","createTime":"2019-07-10T08:12:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T08:12:45.000Z","uid":35221,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"052c9d244aeee4d6a7866f161b9d653d61784757","tid":1303165,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T08:12:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aXP1Fxc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaXP1Fxc.jpg&h=44c14139&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20190710/s00009/854fb919cafa586c54febe1d8af206bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20190710%2Fs00009%2F854fb919cafa586c54febe1d8af206bb.jpg&h=6e49d702&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n連月來《逃犯條例》修訂所引發的爭議中，有網民對「無綫新聞」報道不滿並採取行動，有組織想發起「反紅媒」遊行到將軍澳電視城，更有「追星運動」向廣告商施壓，凡有無綫藝人的活動會到場舉牌「支持」，無綫成為狙擊目標。無綫昨晚在觀塘apm舉行「DSE考生&mdash;放榜前的一個晚上」，突然以「節目調動」為理由決定取消。同時間另一個在屯門V city舉行，有無綫藝人馬國明、江嘉敏等出席的DSE放榜派對，昨午主辦單位亦突然宣布因「場地限制及顧及公眾安全」為原因取消；而網上突然傳出「寶礦力」抽起在無綫播放的廣告。<br />\n<br />\n「寶礦力」多年來請過不少藝人拍廣告，當中最近再婚的翁靜晶曾是代言人，她在社交平台表示時間是40年前，當年15歲的她是在夏威夷拍攝，攝製隊是日本人，廣告後來在台灣播放，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「無巧不成話，當時為我接下這項工作的，是無綫電視。為我傾談廣告條款的，是樂易玲。那一年，我15歲。如今寶礦力抵制無線（綫），真是十年人事幾番新。」</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n（即時娛樂）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20190710/1562734857617/%E3%80%90%E5%8F%8D%E7%B4%85%E5%AA%92-%E3%80%91%E5%82%B3%E5%AF%B6%E7%A4%A6%E5%8A%9B%E6%8A%BD%E7%84%A1%E7%B6%AB%E5%BB%A3%E5%91%8A-%E7%BF%81%E9%9D%9C%E6%99%B615%E6%AD%B2%E6%9B%BE%E5%81%9A%E4%BB%A3%E8%A8%80%E4%BA%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20190710%2F1562734857617%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%258F%258D%25E7%25B4%2585%25E5%25AA%2592-%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%2582%25B3%25E5%25AF%25B6%25E7%25A4%25A6%25E5%258A%259B%25E6%258A%25BD%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%25B6%25AB%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E5%2591%258A-%25E7%25BF%2581%25E9%259D%259C%25E6%2599%25B615%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E6%259B%25BE%25E5%2581%259A%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E8%25A8%2580%25E4%25BA%25BA&d=q18Y%2F9yBacX5GGPSgvrSC2Fzq3Uwi%2FWN07E9MureYdc%3D&h=b8a57bee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20190710%2F1562734857617%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%258F%258D%25E7%25B4%2585%25E5%25AA%2592-%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%2582%25B3%25E5%25AF%25B6%25E7%25A4%25A6%25E5%258A%259B%25E6%258A%25BD%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%25B6%25AB%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E5%2591%258A-%25E7%25BF%2581%25E9%259D%259C%25E6%2599%25B615%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E6%259B%25BE%25E5%2581%259A%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E8%25A8%2580%25E4%25BA%25BA&h=9f7fdfeb\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20190710/1562734857617/%E3%80%90%E5%8F%8D%E7%B4%85%E5%AA%92-%E3%80%91%E5%82%B3%E5%AF%B6%E7%A4%A6%E5%8A%9B%E6%8A%BD%E7%84%A1%E7%B6%AB%E5%BB%A3%E5%91%8A-%E7%BF%81%E9%9D%9C%E6%99%B615%E6%AD%B2%E6%9B%BE%E5%81%9A%E4%BB%A3%E8%A8%80%E4%BA%BA</a></span>"}]}